com.interpss.dstab.algo

Interface IDStabSolver

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractDStabSolver, DStabSolver3SeqImpl, DStabSolverImpl

    public interface IDStabSolver
    A representation of the model object 'ID Stab Solver'. Interface for implementing DStab solver. The intialization() is called at the begining. Then for each simulation step, beforeStep(), nextStep() and afterStep() are called in the performSimulation() method. The beforeStep(), nextStep() and afterStep() could be override to implement a different simulation method.
    See Also:
    DstabAlgorithmPackage.getIDStabSolver()
